    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are not assessed per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3 allowances for Class II devices at MRL 2. CFD hemolysis predictions demonstrate sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case operating conditions. Relative hemolysis index criterion (RH < 1) is appropriate and achievable with demonstrated model accuracy. Assessment team accepts the computational model for the stated COU.",
